dct_title_s: Chart exhibiting the discoveries of the second American Grinnell Expedition in search of Sir John Franklin
dct_alternative_sm: Chart exhibiting the discoveries of the second American Grinnell Expedition in search of Sir John Franklin / by E.K. Kane.
dct_description_sm: 1 map ; 44 x 28 cm., folded to 16 x 10 cm.
Shows locations of various fauna, huts, sea ice and glacciers.
Map is probably from his book "Arctic explorations: the second Grinnell expedition in search of Sir John Franklin, 1853, ’54, ’55".
dcat_keyword_sm: Atlantic States Maps Early works to 1800.
